snippet.title: Marvel End Time Arena - First Impressions
snippet.description:
Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/790650/MARVEL_END_TIME_ARENA/
Marvel End Time Arena is a MOBA type game, which sees Marvel superheroes and villains neck to neck in a destructible interactive environment, kind of like Dota or League of Legends. The game started developing back in 2014. #Marvel #MOBA #Gaming

Sign up here - http://marveleta.game.onstove.com/
Sugi Discord - https://discord.gg/KQQbf9U
